[
  {
    "bookname": "Nahum",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">This is an <st data-num=\"04853\" class=\"\">oracle</st><n id=\"1\" /> about <st data-num=\"05210\" class=\"\">Nineveh</st>; the <st data-num=\"05612\" class=\"\">book</st> of the <st data-num=\"02377\" class=\"\">vision</st> of <st data-num=\"05151\" class=\"\">Nahum</st> the <st data-num=\"0512\" class=\"\">Elkoshite</st>:<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nahum",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> is a <st data-num=\"07072\" class=\"\">zealous</st><n id=\"1\" /> and <st data-num=\"05358\" class=\"\">avenging</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0410\" class=\"\">God</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> is <st data-num=\"05358\" class=\"\">avenging</st> and <st data-num=\"01167\" class=\"\">very</st> <st data-num=\"02534\" class=\"\">angry</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05358\" class=\"\">takes vengeance</st><n id=\"4\" /> against his <st data-num=\"06862\" class=\"\">foes</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">he</st> <st data-num=\"05201\" class=\"\">sustains</st> his <st data-num=\"05201\" class=\"\">rage</st><n id=\"5\" /> against his <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemies</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nahum",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> is <st data-num=\"0750\" class=\"\">slow</st> to <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">anger</st><n id=\"1\" /> but <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">great</st> in <st data-num=\"03581\" class=\"\">power</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> will <st data-num=\"05352\" class=\"\">certainly</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"05352\" class=\"\">allow</st> the wicked<n id=\"4\" /> <st data-num=\"05352\" class=\"\">to go unpunished</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">marches out</st><n id=\"5\" /> in the <st data-num=\"05492\" class=\"\">whirlwind</st> and the <st data-num=\"08183\" class=\"\">raging storm</st>; <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06051\" class=\"\">dark storm clouds</st> billow like <st data-num=\"080\" class=\"\">dust</st> under his <st data-num=\"07272\" class=\"\">feet</st>.<n id=\"6\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nahum",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"01605\" class=\"\">shouts a battle cry</st><n id=\"1\" /> against the <st data-num=\"03220\" class=\"\">sea</st><n id=\"2\" /> and <st data-num=\"03001\" class=\"\">makes</st> it <st data-num=\"03001\" class=\"\">dry up</st>;<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">he makes <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05104\" class=\"\">rivers</st><n id=\"4\" /><st data-num=\"02717\" class=\"\"> run dry</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01316\" class=\"\">Bashan</st> and <st data-num=\"03760\" class=\"\">Carmel</st> <st data-num=\"0536\" class=\"\">wither</st>;<n id=\"5\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"06525\" class=\"\">blossom</st> of <st data-num=\"03844\" class=\"\">Lebanon</st> <st data-num=\"0536\" class=\"\">withers</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nahum",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"02022\" class=\"\">mountains</st> <st data-num=\"07493\" class=\"\">tremble</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">before</st> him;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"01389\" class=\"\">hills</st> <st data-num=\"04127\" class=\"\">convulse</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st> is <st data-num=\"07582\" class=\"\">laid waste</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> him<p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"08398\" class=\"\">world</st> and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> its <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">inhabitants</st><n id=\"4\" /> are laid waste.<n id=\"5\" /></p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nahum",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">No one</st> can <st data-num=\"06440 05975\">withstand</st><n id=\"1\" /> his <st data-num=\"02195\" class=\"\">indignation</st>!<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">No one</st> can <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">resist</st><n id=\"3\" /> his <st data-num=\"02740\" class=\"\">fierce</st> <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">anger</st>!<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">His <st data-num=\"02534\" class=\"\">wrath</st> is <st data-num=\"05413\" class=\"\">poured out</st> like volcanic <st data-num=\"0784\" class=\"\">fire</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06697\" class=\"\">boulders</st> are <st data-num=\"05422\" class=\"\">broken up</st><n id=\"5\" /> as he <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">approaches</st>.<n id=\"6\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nahum",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> is <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">good</st><n id=\"1\" />\u2014<p class=\"poetry\">indeed,<n id=\"2\" /> he is a <st data-num=\"04581\" class=\"\">fortress</st><n id=\"3\" /> in <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">time</st> of <st data-num=\"06869\" class=\"\">distress</st>,<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and he <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">protects</st><n id=\"5\" /> those who <st data-num=\"02620\" class=\"\">seek refuge</st><n id=\"6\" /> in him.</p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nahum",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">But with an <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">overwhelming</st> <st data-num=\"07858\" class=\"\">flood</st><n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">he will <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">make</st> a <st data-num=\"03617\" class=\"\">complete end</st> of <st data-num=\"04725\" class=\"\">Nineveh</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">he will <st data-num=\"07291\" class=\"\">drive</st><n id=\"3\" /> his <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemies</st> into <st data-num=\"02822\" class=\"\">darkness</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nahum",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">Whatever</st><n id=\"1\" /> you <st data-num=\"02803\" class=\"\">plot</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">against</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">he</st> will <st data-num=\"03617 06213\">completely destroy</st>!<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06869\" class=\"\">Distress</st><n id=\"4\" /> will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">arise</st><n id=\"5\" /> a <st data-num=\"06471\" class=\"\">second time</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nahum",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Surely</st> they will be totally <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">consumed</st><n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">like</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"05440\" class=\"\">entangled</st> <st data-num=\"05518\" class=\"\">thornbushes</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">like the <st data-num=\"05435\" class=\"\">drink</st> of <st data-num=\"05433\" class=\"\">drunkards</st>,<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">like <st data-num=\"04390\" class=\"\">very</st><n id=\"5\" /> <st data-num=\"03002\" class=\"\">dry</st> <st data-num=\"07179\" class=\"\">stubble</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nahum",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">From</st> you, O Nineveh,<n id=\"1\" /> one has <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">marched forth</st> who <st data-num=\"02803\" class=\"\">plots</st> <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">evil</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">against</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>,<p class=\"poetry\">a <st data-num=\"01100\" class=\"\">wicked</st> military <st data-num=\"03289\" class=\"\">strategist</st>.<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nahum",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">This is what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st>:<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">Even though</st><n id=\"2\" /> they are <st data-num=\"08003\" class=\"\">powerful</st><n id=\"3\" />\u2014<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">what is more</st>,<n id=\"4\" /> even though their army is <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">numerous</st><n id=\"5\" />\u2014<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">nevertheless</st>,<n id=\"6\" /> they will be <st data-num=\"01494\" class=\"\">destroyed</st><n id=\"7\" /> and <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">trickle away</st>!<n id=\"8\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Although I <st data-num=\"06031\" class=\"\">afflicted</st> you,<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"06031\" class=\"\">afflict</st> you <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"05750\" class=\"\">more</st>.<n id=\"9\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nahum",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">And <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">now</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> I will <st data-num=\"07665\" class=\"\">break</st> Assyria\u2019s<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"04132\" class=\"\">yoke bar</st><n id=\"3\" /> from your <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">neck</st>;<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"05423\" class=\"\">tear apart</st> the <st data-num=\"04147\" class=\"\">shackles</st><n id=\"5\" /> that are on you.\u201d<n id=\"6\" /></p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nahum",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">issued a decree</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">against</st> you:<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cYour <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">dynasty</st> will <st data-num=\"02232\">come</st> to an <st data-num=\"03808 05750\">end</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"03772\" class=\"\">destroy</st> the <st data-num=\"06459\" class=\"\">idols</st> and <st data-num=\"04541\" class=\"\">images</st> in the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temples</st> of your <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">gods</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"08074\" class=\"\">desecrate</st><n id=\"3\" /> your <st data-num=\"06913\" class=\"\">grave</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> you are <st data-num=\"07043\" class=\"\">accursed</st>!\u201d<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Nahum",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">(2:1)<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Look</st>! A <st data-num=\"01319\" class=\"\">herald</st> is <st data-num=\"07272\" class=\"\">running</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> the <st data-num=\"02022\" class=\"\">mountains</st>!<p class=\"poetry\">A messenger is <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">proclaiming</st> <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">deliverance</st>:<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"02287\" class=\"\">Celebrate</st> your <st data-num=\"02282\" class=\"\">sacred festivals</st>, O <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07999\" class=\"\">Fulfill</st> your <st data-num=\"05088\" class=\"\">sacred vows</st> to praise God!<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">never</st> <st data-num=\"05750\" class=\"\">again</st><n id=\"5\" /> <st data-num=\"03254\" class=\"\">will</st> the <st data-num=\"01100\" class=\"\">wicked</st><n id=\"6\" /> Assyrians<n id=\"7\" /> <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">invade</st><n id=\"8\" /> you;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">they</st><n id=\"9\" /> have been <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">completely</st> <st data-num=\"03772\" class=\"\">destroyed</st>.\u201d<n id=\"10\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  }
]